data.description: This immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home features almost 2200 sqft. of living space and a luxurious sparkling pool with sundeck and waterfall. Fenced in backyard includes lush landscaping, fruit trees, and a covered lanai. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and an abundance of cabinets. The large master bedroom is one of two ensuites. Both ensuites have their own exterior door to the patio. Perfect for in-laws or guests. Additional features include recessed ceilings with decorative lighting, handcrafted stone wall, crown molding, indoor laundry, Wi-Fi compatible switches and more. Easy access to the highway and turnpike. Close to shopping, dining, and The Mets stadium.
